    <subfield code="a">Worm Algorithm for the <math altimg="si1.gif" display="inline" overflow="scroll"><mi mathvariant="double-struck">C</mi><msup><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>N</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math> Model</subfield>
